American Mortgage & Investment Services (AMAISI) is a dynamic yet stable company which generates millions of dollars in financing volume per month.  We provide hundreds of financing programs including Fannie Mae, Freddie Mac, FHA, SBA, and many other commercial and residential portfolio programs. AMAISI is proud to have been chosen as one of less than 50 lenders nationwide for Fannie Mae’s pilot program, Choice Finder, which was designed to help promote home ownership in emerging markets, along with implementing technological enhancements in the Desktop Originator FannieMae online underwriting engine.  We strive to find the best financing for your unique residential or commercial needs. It is our goal and commitment to represent the highest levels of  industry professionalism. 
 
Our adherence to strict professional disciplines and ethical standards has allowed us to become a preferred lender of a number of companies, organizations, and individuals.  Maintaining BEST BUSINESS PRACTICES as it applies to customer service is our top priority, which has distinguished us as an established business leader in our service communities.  AMAISI follows a TRIPLE NET philosophy that designates corporate care towards not only the business aspect of a company, but also its responsibility towards society and the enviornment. We believe that a successful company should not only have a positive business impact, but should also be a beneficial community presence.  GCAAR, Habitat for Humanity, FTOP, Reach Green, and The University of Maryland are some of the organizations that we are either a preferred lender of, or have worked with on joint initiatives. 
 





Helping Build Home and Business Ownership Dreams...With Social and Environmental Responsibility!




